    :meth:`Gst.Clock.id_wait`. To receive a callback when the specific time is reached
    in the clock use :meth:`Gst.Clock.id_wait_async`. Both these calls can be
    interrupted with the :meth:`Gst.Clock.id_unschedule` call. If the blocking wait is
    unscheduled a return value of :data:`Gst.ClockReturn.UNSCHEDULED` is returned.

